<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Fitchew" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Fitchew,</orth> the pole-cat: <bibl n="shak. tro 5.1.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 1, 67</bibl>. Thought to be very amorous: <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.124" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 124</bibl>. Hence a term for a wanton woman: <bibl n="shak. oth 4.1.150" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 1, 150</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>